4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Course that aims to transform students into web development experts. The course covers a wide range of skills and technologies necessary for building applications from scratch. With a duration of 18 weeks, students will master the most sought-after programming languages like Python and JavaScript.

The program includes classes three times a week, and students can choose between English and Spanish for the syllabus and content. No previous coding skills or advanced math are required to enroll in the course. Upon completion, students will receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate.

The instructors for the course include Rodolfo Campos, a Senior Solutions Architect at VMware, with expertise in Linux, Java, SQL, and Blockchain. Gabriel Salinas, also a Senior Solutions Architect at VMware, brings his experience as a Sophisticated Software Systems Engineer.

By joining the Full Stack Developer Course at 4Geeks Academy, students have the opportunity to gain game-changing hands-on experience and reshape their mindset to succeed in the tech industry.

